   <concept id="FAR_52_251_1" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">52.251-1</ph> Government Supply Sources.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p " id="d3773e8">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="51.107.dita#FAR_51_107"
                     base="i1066432"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">51.107</xref>
            </ph>, insert the following clause:</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" id="d3773e14">Government Supply Sources <ph outputclass="SmCaps" class="- topic/ph ">(Apr 2012)</ph>
         </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The Contracting Officer may issue the Contractor an authorization to use Government supply sources in the performance of this contract. Title to all property acquired by the Contractor under such an authorization shall vest in the Government unless otherwise specified in the contract. The provisions of the clause at FAR <xref href="52.245-1.dita#FAR_52_245_1"
                  base="i1047486"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">52.245-1</xref>, Government Property, apply to all property acquired under such authorization</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Endofclause">(End of clause)</p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
